Name: What's Inside??
About the game: 'What's Inside??' is a light-hearted comedic romance visual novel for all ages.. Follow the adventures of four friends as they discover love and acceptance whilst unravelling a curious and sinister mystery.. Player choice determines the path through the narrative and influences character disposition.. Can the girls overcome the challenges of life and love whilst potentially saving all of humanity in the process?? Discover what's truly inside!!
